    class MyCommonModel

    This class defines the common functionality of the model in MVP architectural pattern
    Manages the data, logic and rules of the MVP architectural pattern

    Data structure :
  • mapMaze3D - hold the Maze3D with name
  • mapSolution - hold the Solution of the Maze3D with name

    Data member :
  • Controller
  • ExecutorService - manage the threads
